{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Doodle Harmony Idle Merge is a relaxing idle merging game, where you buy Doodles and generate them in real time, then sell them to turn a profit or keep them around to earn money.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949230/extras/Doodle_Harmony_Idle_Merge_Demo_2024-09-19_17-32-02_1.gif?t=1728917589\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfa8Doodle Merging: Merge two identical Doodles to upgrade them.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udcb0 Passive Income Generation: Your Doodles earn money for you automatically.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udd04Offline Progress: Keep earning money even when you're not playing.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udd13Unlock New Doodles: Explore a variety of characters to merge and expand your Collection.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udfc6Achievements: Unlock achievements as you progress through the game.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83d\udcfbRadio System: Radio System to choose your music.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\ud83c\udf11Dark Mode: Chose between a light mode and a dark mode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\u2699\ufe0f Upgrades: Enhance your gameplay with upgrades!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>\ud83d\udee0\ufe0f Skills: Use special skills that speed up your progression in the game!</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2949230/extras/upgrades2.gif?t=1728917589\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Merge Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2949230/8296192ae5b17f260e383e9c94b4140ae0bd5aba.jpg"},{"name":"M